  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink283-kilavi">tōḻi vāyil maṟukkavum talaimakaṉ āṟṟāmai kaṇṭu talaimakaḷ vāyil nēra vavaṉ paḷḷiyiṭattāṉāy iruntuḻip pukka tōḻi kūṟiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          As the confidante refused entry [to the hero], and as the heroine granted [him] entry on seeing his inability, what the confidante who entered, said when the hero was in his resting place.          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink283">
<l>vaṉkaṭ kāṉavaṉ meṉcoṉ maṭamakaḷ</l>
<l>puṉpula mayakkat tuḻuta vēṉaṟ</l>
<l>paimpuṟac ciṟukiḷi kaṭiyu nāṭa</l>
<l>periya kūṟi nīppiṉum</l>
<l>poyvalaip paṭūum peṇṭutavap palavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where</l>
        <l>the soft-spoken naïve daughter </l>
        <l>of the strong forest man,</l>
        <l>chases away the small green-backed parakeets</l>
        <l>from the millet grown in the mixture of low[-lying] soils—</l>
        <l rend="space">even if you speak grand words and leave,</l>
        <l>many women fall</l>
        <l>into your net of lies.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
